description: Live in the heart of downtown Seattle at The Elektra! This quiet east-facing 2-bedroom, 1-bath condo is FULLY FURNISHED and elevator-served. Hardwood floors. No pet restrictions & short-term rentals allowed—ideal for flexible living or investment. Enjoy secure garage parking next door, concierge service, & resident amenities including a recreation lounge with pool table and TV. HOA dues cover heat, water, sewer, trash, security, and maintenance for exceptional value. Onsite laundry & unit has hookups. Enjoy roof top city views. Walkable to shops, dining, and entertainment. Prime location to Convention Center, Amazon, and Westlake center. Priced below assessed value—an unbeatable opportunity, especially with the 2026 World Cup approaching!
